org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters

Class RFSurveySpecStopTrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.RFSurveySpecStopTrigger

  • public class RFSurveySpecStopTrigger
extends TLVParameter
    This parameter defines the stop trigger for RF Survey operations. See also LLRP Specification Section 10.2.3.1 and LLRP Specification Section 16.2.4.3.1 .
